; Souls Style Looting - place in: <Game>\Data\SKSE\Plugins\SoulsStyleLooting.ini (same folder as the DLL)
; Optional: SoulsStyleLoot_TypeIcons.json in the same folder maps keyword EditorID to icon paths (e.g. "OCF_WeapTypeSword1H": "assets/weapons/sword.png").
; SafetyKey: Virtual key code held to open normal container menu. 0 = disabled. 16=Shift, 17=Ctrl, 18=Alt. MCM overrides.
; LootDisplaySeconds: Fallback display time (2-15). Used when not cycling.
; LootCycleDelaySeconds: Seconds each item is shown before cycling to the next (0.5-10). Default 2.0.
; LootCloseKeyCode: Virtual key to close loot UI after last item (activate key). Default 0x45 (E).
; LootUIView: which HTML view to use. Default SoulsStyleLoot/index.html.
; - SoulsStyleLoot/index.html: current single-item cycle view
; - SoulsStyleLoot/index_list.html: list view (shows all items at once)
; DropChancePercent: chance that a corpse drops any random loot (0-100). MCM DarkSoulsPickUpChances overrides.
; Tier: common -> legendary. Type: weapon, armor, ammo, misc, book. All values 0-100 (percentage).
; EnchantedWeaponTierXChance / EnchantedArmorTierXChance: extra gate that only applies if the item is already enchanted (base form enchantment).
; Example: if an enchanted weapon is Tier2 and EnchantedWeaponTier2Chance=40, it has a 40% chance to make it into the drop candidates
; (after it already passed the normal Tier/Type rolls). Unenchanted weapons/armor are unaffected.
;
; --- Balanced preset (below) ---
; Corpse drops loot 75% of the time. Common items often, legendary rare. Weapons/armor a bit rarer than misc, books rarer.
[Settings]
SafetyKey=16
LootDisplaySeconds=5.0
LootCycleDelaySeconds=2.0
LootCloseKeyCode=69
LootUIView=SoulsStyleLoot/index.html
DropChancePercent=75
Tier0DropChance=100
Tier1DropChance=65
Tier2DropChance=35
Tier3DropChance=15
WeaponDropChance=85
ArmorDropChance=85
AmmoDropChance=90
MiscDropChance=95
BookDropChance=50
EnchantedWeaponTier0Chance=20
EnchantedWeaponTier1Chance=30
EnchantedWeaponTier2Chance=45
EnchantedWeaponTier3Chance=65
EnchantedArmorTier0Chance=20
EnchantedArmorTier1Chance=30
EnchantedArmorTier2Chance=45
EnchantedArmorTier3Chance=65
